                                           PURPLE CHATBOT
An interactive chatbot application built with the elegance of Dash and the power of Google Generative AI. This application not only facilitates conversations but also enables data-driven insights through dynamic visualizations and CSV processing.


 Key Features

✨ Interactive Chat: Engage with a bot in a stylish chat interface.
✨ Data Visualization: Upload CSV files to generate beautiful graphs on the fly.
✨ AI-Powered Responses: Leverage cutting-edge AI for dynamic and meaningful interactions.
✨ PDF Generation: Convert CSV data into professional-quality PDFs for easy sharing.
✨ Clean and Modern UI: Designed with a vibrant purple theme and responsive layout.


🔧 Prerequisites

Ensure your system meets these requirements before proceeding:
Python 3.7+
Internet connection for AI integration


🛠️ Installation

Follow these steps to set up the application:
Clone the Repository:
git clone https://github.com/your-repo/chatbot-purple-theme.git
cd chatbot-purple-theme
Set Up a Virtual Environment:
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate   # Linux/Mac  
venv\Scripts\activate      # Windows 
Install Dependencies:
pip install -r requirements.txt
Configure API Key:
Create a .env file in the project directory with your API key:
env
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_api_key_here


▶️ Running the Application
Start the server:
python app.py


Open your browser and visit:
http://127.0.0.1:8050  


🎨 Usage

Chat with the Bot:
Type a message and click Send to start a conversation.

Upload a CSV File:
Click the 📂 button to upload a CSV file for analysis.

Generate Graphs:
Request various graph types such as bar, line, scatter, and pie.

Convert CSV to PDF:
Ask the bot to create a PDF from your CSV data.


📊 Supported Graph Types

Graph Type	Description	Example Use Case
Bar Chart	Compare quantities across categories	Sales data comparison
Line Graph	Visualize trends over time	Stock price movements
Scatter Plot	Show relationships between variables	Correlation analysis
Pie Chart	Display proportions	Market share breakdown
Histogram	Analyze data distribution	Frequency of test scores
Box Plot	Display data variability	Outlier detection in datasets


🌟 Future Enhancements

Multi-Language Support: Chat in different languages.
Advanced Graph Customizations: Provide detailed graph settings.
Real-Time Data Integration: Fetch live data for dynamic insights.


